  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the prevalence of hypertension among citizens of
      Holstebro, Denmark aged 55-64 years, including both the well treated, the untreated and the
      insufficiently treated, and to estimate the prevalence of white coat and masked hypertension
      using home blood pressure measurements with telemedical data transmission.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
